<Title>广东一家庭作坊火灾 致11人窒息死亡</Title>

<ReportTime type="relTime">2014年03月27日</ReportTime> 　　浙江在线新闻网站
<Content>
<Paragraph>
<Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time type="relTime" tid="t1">3月26日下午1时27分</Time>，<Location lid="l1">普宁市军埠镇一家庭作坊(主要生产内衣)</Location>发生<Denoter type="emergency" did="d1">火灾</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e2"><Time type="relTime" tid="t2">1时54分</Time>，<Object oid="o2">火势</Object>被<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d2">扑灭</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e3"><Time type="relTime" tid="t3">截至发稿时</Time>，<Location lid="l3">现场</Location><Denoter type="operation" did="d3">解救</Denoter>出<Participant oid="o3">17名群众</Participant></Event>，
<Event eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">15人</Participant>不同程度<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">受伤</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e5">送<Location type="destination" lid="l5">医院</Location><Denoter type="operation" did="d5">救治</Denoter></Event>，
</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e6"><Denoter type="action" did="d6">接报</Denoter></Event>后，
<Event eid="e7">揭阳市委、市政府高度重视，<Participant sid="s7">揭阳市委书记陈绿平</Participant>迅速作出<Denoter type="operation" did="d7">批示</Denoter>
</Event>，
要求
<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">普宁市及有关部门</Participant>全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d8">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o8">搜救</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e9">尽全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d9">抢救</Denoter><Participant oid="o9">伤员</Participant></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time type="relTime" tid="t10">同时</Time>，立刻<Denoter type="operation" did="d10">指派</Denoter><Participant sid="o10,s11">揭阳市委常委、常务副市长陈澄民，揭阳副市长、市公安局局长谢耀琪</Participant></Event>
<Event eid="e11"><Denoter type="movement" did="d11">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l11">现场</Location></Event>，
<Event eid="e12">并<Denoter type="operation" did="d12">成立</Denoter><Object oid="o12">事故处置小组</Object></Event>
负责事故处置工作。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">揭阳市消防部门</Participant><Denoter type="action" did="d13">出动</Denoter><Object oid="o13">7台消防车</Object>，<Participant oid="o13">45名消防员</Participant></Event>
<Event eid="e14">立即<Denoter type="movement" did="d14">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l14">现场</Location></Event>
<Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d15">灭火</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">普宁市党政主要负责同志</Participant>第一时间<Denoter type="movement" did="d16">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" did="d17">现场</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e18">全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d18">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o18">灭火和人员救治工作</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>                   

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>目前，相关善后工作正有序进行中。</Sentence></Paragraph>

